ref:_00D7091pB._500Q000Ned0e:ref

Mike my apologies, I see my email reply attached to this ticket.  I used to see the actual ticket number in the subject line of emails. 

Anyway, I just learned as I looked into this more the "Direct_Permission" result of the job is over 1 million+ rows and apparently, I just needed to be patient.   It finally completed without crashing the console app.

So, I was looking for two specific AD groups to see where they might have been applied, but my filtering on the 'Trustee column' didn't return any results. I assume these groups are NOT applied anywhere.

Question - Do you have any documentation about what the 'FSAA_GROUP_Direct_permissions' (under Direct Permissions job) collects?  This article does not reference it.
https://helpcenter.netwrix.com/bundle/StealthAUDIT_11.5/page/Content/StealthAUDIT/Job_Groups/FS_Job_Group/2.Direct_Permission/2.Direct_Permissions_Job_Group.htm
